\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\sa360\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Below the index card is the notes area, where you can jot down anything relating to the document that you don\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t want in the text itself, such as ideas and problems.}
